title: Hear what Nick Saban had to say after Alabama's 19-14 win over Tennessee
text: Nick Saban spoke to the media after Alabama's 19-14 victory over Tennessee. Watch the video above to hear what Alabama's coach had to say regarding why Alabama "didn't have a lot of energy", their resilience, what they will work on during the coming bye week, and much more.
